---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro"
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Shipping & Delivery Policy"
  description="Overview of Botyoo's digital product delivery timelines and fulfillment details."
>
  <h1 class="text-foreground mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">Shipping & Delivery Policy</h1>

  <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">
    At botyoo.com, all services are delivered digitally and instantly after
    successful payment. There are no physical shipments.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Instant Delivery</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">All services purchased on botyoo.com are delivered instantly after successful payment. You will receive confirmation and access to your service immediately via email or directly in your Botyoo account.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. Delivery Methods</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Access your purchased service via:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Your Botyoo account dashboard</li>
      <li>Email notifications sent immediately after purchase</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. Delivery Issues</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">If you do not receive access to your service instantly, please:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Check your email spam/junk folder</li>
      <li>Ensure your Botyoo account email is correct</li>
      <li>Contact our support team immediately for assistance</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">📧 <strong class="text-foreground">hevin@botyoo.com</strong></p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
